{"tid":2304868,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"全球現金「失蹤」案","createTime":"2020-11-29T07:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T05:05:49.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"80158875c9680dd24bb1933ae9ef0004ad4ba33d","tid":2304868,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/rsz_gettyimages-99978248.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2Frsz_gettyimages-99978248.jpg&h=d93f7cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銀行比以往發行更多鈔票，但現金似乎正在地球上消失。<span class=\"red\">各地中央銀行都不知它們「失蹤」的原因或去向，紛紛試圖破解這個金融之謎</span>。因應信用卡及手機支付愈趨流行，各地社會及公司開始推行無現金化，事情更是撲朔迷離。不過，原因可能很簡單 &mdash;&mdash; 在澳洲、瑞士、德國等地，都有不少人囤積現金。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國聯邦儲備局，去年流通的美元總值 1.7 兆，較 2013 年的 1.2 兆為高。儲備局經濟學家 Ruth Judson 前年發表論文指，約有 60% 在市面流通的所有面額美元，以及 75% 的 100 美元鈔票，在 2016 年底前流出國外，合共約有 9,000 億美元。文中指出，此舉能為抵禦經濟動盪提供一定保護，尤其是在一些金融體系不穩的國家。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲儲備銀行 &mdash;&mdash; 澳洲央行行長 Philip Lowe 則表示，就經濟規模而言，澳洲鈔票的存量接近 50 年來的最高水平。最近他就在墨爾本出席一個晚餐會，向在場人士展示新發行鈔票，他估計，平均每名澳洲人手持約值 2,000 澳元的已發行鈔票。「我自己的話，手頭上可沒這個金額。」<br />\n<br />\n銀行家關心現金的去向，<span class=\"red\">因為央行需要掌握市面有多少現金，以免發鈔過多，帶來通脹的風險</span>。然而，不少人故意「作對」。近日一批建築工人在澳洲黃金海岸一個工地，就挖到一個估計裝了 14 萬美元的包裹；在德國，一名男子把逾 50 萬歐元現金塞進一個壞掉的鍋爐，朋友卻在他度假時修理這鍋爐，令錢全被燒掉，他因此控告朋友但被判敗訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/rsz_gettyimages-485310534.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2Frsz_gettyimages-485310534.jpg&h=482a181d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/12/17/global-cash-disappearing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F12%2F17%2Fglobal-cash-disappearing%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR8mKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=1cdb2fa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/12/17/global-cash-disappearing/</a>"},{"pid":"0bb4a55d7f637298fb0367cff62b41c848e5a6b2","tid":2304868,"uid":103434,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:19:08.000Z","msg":"去哂林女士屋企"},{"pid":"9c92a65cb7f38f8c8184552f5b877684a3b2e772","tid":2304868,"uid":156144,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:59:33.000Z","msg":"Cash is king? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f512d3eb2ebf9a6267643975e462eaafa9636e1","tid":2304868,"uid":168911,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:09:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">2019-12-17</span>"},{"pid":"e3543ccf7ddcc332543c827178ba714318381d50","tid":2304868,"uid":117947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:10:11.000Z","msg":"呢排凍，燒緊啲銀紙取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd3bd1b60e2a2fa21c64f3c7bc4d3a1d13497e3","tid":2304868,"uid":200202,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最尾一個錢冇左frd又冇埋"},{"pid":"fd9620c9b4c188fb45b37884bf254ce1541b93ae","tid":2304868,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0bb4a55d7f637298fb0367cff62b41c848e5a6b2","tid":2304868,"uid":103434,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:19:08.000Z","msg":"去哂林女士屋企"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"咁就撚到連登仔，樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e711757543daae6d5f4d37f92c99e808fbdca3a2","tid":2304868,"uid":28547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b383